OL,3,CPride of Britain 2026: Nominate a hero
OL,4,Cto be Granada's Fundraiser of the Year
OL,6,FThe Daily Mirror Pride of Britain
OL,7,FAwards has been honouring the nation's
OL,8,Funsung heroes since 1999, and Granada
OL,9,FReports is now looking for its next
OL,10,FRegional Fundraiser of the Year.
OL,12,FThe Pride of Britain ceremony is one
OL,13,Fof the biggest events in the showbiz
OL,14,Fcalendar, and a chance to celebrate
OL,15,Fthose who have made a real difference
OL,16,Fin their community.
