OL,3,CPride of Britain 2026: Nominate a hero
OL,4,Cto be Granada's Fundraiser of the Year
OL,6,FIndividuals and groups can be
OL,7,Fnominated for ITV Granada's Regional
OL,8,FFundraiser of the Year, and from the
OL,9,Ffour finalists one winner will be
OL,10,Finvited to attend a glitzy awards
OL,11,Fceremony in London.
OL,13,FLast year, Shaun and Philippa Stirrup
OL,14,Fwere named Granada's Regional
OL,15,FFundraiser of the Year for their work
OL,16,Fproviding support and resources to
OL,17,Fgrieving parents.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
