OL,3,CPride of Britain 2026: Nominate a hero
OL,4,Cto be Granada's Fundraiser of the Year
OL,6,FThe couple started the Milly-Rose
OL,7,FStirrup Foundation after the death of
OL,8,Ftheir six-year-old daughter in
OL,9,FFebruary 2023.
OL,11,FThe charity aims to "create a legacy
OL,12,Fin Milly-Rose" and "relieve the
OL,13,Fdistress of parents and families who
OL,14,Fhave suffered this immeasurable loss."
OL,16,FPhilippa said: "We lost Milly during
OL,17,F(resuscitation). It was very sterile,
OL,18,Fthere were tubes everywhere and
OL,19,Fintense lighting, and I think our aim
OL,20,Fis to provide a room that's a bit more
OL,21,Fcomforting."
OL,26,@yD@ApmyD@Opn
